# Website Code agent

**Agent name:** Website Code  
**Prompt:** `agents/WebsiteCode/CONTINUE.md`  
**Build state:** `agents/WebsiteCode/BUILD-STATE.md`  
**Port:** 3004 (`npm run dev`)

## Scope

ShopSite microsites, shop editor (`/marketing/website`), Master CRM websites pipeline (`/platform/websites`), custom domain middleware.

## Not in scope

- ShopRally marketing site: `src/app/(marketing)/`
- CRM shell, RO workspace, dashboard
- SEO Autopilot module (coordinate on shared domain/GSC files)

Update `agents/WebsiteCode/BUILD-STATE.md` after meaningful progress.
